Location & Directions
17306 NW 112th Blvd.
Alachua, FL 32615
FROM GAINESVILLE
Go north on US 441 (from the Highway Patrol Station at 34th Street go approximately 12 miles) until you come to the 1st traffic light in the city of Alachua.
At the intersection of SR 235 & US 441, turn right on SR 235 (north) and go 2.5 miles.
On the left you will see the temple entrance, “Hare Krishna Temple.” Turn left into the driveway.
FROM INTERSTATE I-75
Take exit 399. At the end of the ramp, turn left on US 441.
Proceed south on US 441 for approximately 1.5 miles until you come to the 3rd traffic light in the city of Alachua, the intersection of SR 235 & US 441.
Turn left on SR 235 (north) and go 2.5 miles. On the left you will see the temple enterance, “Hare Krishna Temple.” Turn left into the driveway.
